snippet.title: Kizuna AI - Touch the Beat! -  Release Data Announce Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
snippet.description:
Kizuna AI - Touch the Beat!

A rhythm game you play with Kizuna AI! Coming to PS4 / PS5!

PS5 version supports PSVR2, and it will be released at the same time as PSVR2.

#ps5 #ps4 #ps5games #ps4games #psvr2
